{"tid":855795,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"騰訊跌出全球十大公司之一 被埃克森美孚取代","createTime":"2018-10-10T09:09:08.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-10T09:17:59.000Z","uid":28765,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"71602c5ef3b422b22a70ab3cb2e25a26d2f13cf2","tid":855795,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T09:09:08.000Z","msg":"【彭博】-- 騰訊控股又有壞消息：這家中國網際網路巨頭已不再是全球十大公司之一。<br />\n<br />\n騰訊控股市值在今年蒸發逾2,000億美元，超過了全球其他任何一家公司。之後，埃克森美孚石油取代騰訊，成為按市值排名的全球十大公司之一。當騰訊股價在1月創下歷史新高時，這家總部位於深圳的公司曾與蘋果公司、Alphabet Inc.、微軟和亞馬遜公司一道成為全球五大公司。<br />\n<br />\n截至今年1月底，騰訊控股股票和首次公開募股時相比曾帶來超過67,000%的回報，但之後因為一連串的壞消息，股價在今年急轉直下，其中包括罕見的利潤下降以及中國監管機構限制網絡遊戲的新舉措。自1月23日以來，騰訊控股在香港股市下挫近40%，周三連續第九天下跌，有望創出有史以來最糟糕的表現。截至13:42，該股下跌0.9%。<br />\n<br />\n總部位於聖巴巴拉的Lead Edge Capital的創始合伙人Mitchell Green表示，隨著投資者開始恐慌，該股可能會繼續遭拋售。Lead Edge Capital管理著15億美元的資產。<br />\n<br />\n騰訊目前的市值為3,530億美元，而埃克森美孚的市值為3,650億美元。<br />\n<br />\n原文標題Tencent Is No Longer One of the World&rsquo;s 10 Biggest Companies (1)<br />\n<br />\n--聯合報導 Lulu Yilun Chen.<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/news/%E9%A8%B0%E8%A8%8A%E4%B8%8D%E5%86%8D%E6%98%AF%E5%85%A8%E7%90%83%E5%8D%81%E5%A4%A7%E5%85%AC%E5%8F%B8%E4%B9%8B-065235145.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.yahoo.com%2Fnews%2F%25E9%25A8%25B0%25E8%25A8%258A%25E4%25B8%258D%25E5%2586%258D%25E6%2598%25AF%25E5%2585%25A8%25E7%2590%2583%25E5%258D%2581%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E5%2585%25AC%25E5%258F%25B8%25E4%25B9%258B-065235145.html&d=asgtric5%2Fy7YLeUHCcb7Wr5jdjnviJyhTm2mNdHk1vQ%3D&h=7cce0817\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/news/%E9%A8%B0%E8%A8%8A%E4%B8%8D%E5%86%8D%E6%98%AF%E5%85%A8%E7%90%83%E5%8D%81%E5%A4%A7%E5%85%AC%E5%8F%B8%E4%B9%8B-065235145.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static01.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2175000/2178687/1009_1024.PNG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic01.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2175000%2F2178687%2F1009_1024.PNG&h=0398eca3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8155fa37371fdfec750b61e066851eb25ee800b9","tid":855795,"uid":35014,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T09:09:56.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4ba1cb5a165bb47cd22cdc635e6d8c72a0951573","tid":855795,"uid":36238,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T09:12:00.000Z","msg":"黎智英<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"137dd9c25c6cd1bb547705441711c4a54abab794","tid":855795,"uid":59283,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T09:13:46.000Z","msg":"幾時到阿里巴巴<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"efe69fc32627862d3b551903aed1873db962698f","tid":855795,"uid":136431,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T09:15:46.000Z","msg":"蒸發兩千億美金好閒啫<br />\n一個半人工島咋嘛<br />\n香港人貼返俾你"},{"pid":"2669eb7c10d530a0f53bd0475907a4f0d427c1e5","tid":855795,"uid":197540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T09:17:59.000Z","msg":"#7 下個仲唔輪你? <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}